data.description: SUPER SHARP 3 BEDROOM GEORGIAN JUST STEPS TO SOUGHT AFTER FIELD ELEMENTARY AND LESS THAN 1 MILE TO DOWNTOWN ELMHURST. THIS CHARMING AND UPDATED HOME BOASTS A SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM WITH LARGE BAY WINDOW. SEPARATE DINING ROOM WITH DOOR THAT LEADS TO LARGE NEWER DECK. UPDATED KITCHEN WITH STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS AND PLENTY OF STORAGE. KITCHEN WINDOW VIEWS TO THE BACKYARD. GLEAMING HARDWOOD FLOORS ON THE FIRST AND SECOND FLOOR. MASTER BEDROOM WITH OFFICE NOOK AND 2 CLOSESTS.  FINISHED BASEMENT FOR ADDED LIVING SPACE WITH BUILT-INS AND LAUNDRY ROOM WITH PLENTY OF STORAGE. MANY UPDATES WITHIN THE LAST 10 YEARS: WINDOWS, ROOF, ENTRY DOORS, DECK, HOT WATER HEATER, WASHER/ DRYER, DISHWASHER. WALK TO SCHOOL, TRAIN, TOWN AND CLOSE TO HIGHWAYS. A MUST SEE!!
